Quick Start Commands:

  # find available emulators
  emulator -list-avds

  # 1. Start the emulator
  emulator -avd Pixel_8 &

  # 2. Wait for it to boot (optional but recommended)
  adb wait-for-device

  # 3. Install on emulator
  adb install -r platforms/android/app/build/outputs/apk/release/app-release.apk

  # 4. Run the game
    adb shell am start -n com.wardeck.game/.MainActivity

  One-liner for convenience:

  emulator -avd Medium_Tablet & sleep 30 && adb install -r app/build/outputs/apk/release/app-release.apk && adb shell am start -n
  com.wardeck.game/.MainActivity

  Useful additional commands:

  # List available emulators
  emulator -list-avds

  # Check if emulator is running
  adb devices

  # Uninstall the game
  adb uninstall com.wardeck.game

  # Take a screenshot
  adb exec-out screencap -p > screenshot.png

  # Close the emulator
  adb emu kill
